import styled from "styled-components"
import { colors, fontSize, fontWeight } from "../variables"

const FormWrapper = styled.form`
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
`

const FormLabel = styled.label`
  font-size: ${fontSize.text};
  color: ${colors.PRIMARY};
  font-weight: ${fontWeight.bold};
`

const FormInput = styled.input``

const FormButton = styled.button``

const FormTextArea = styled.textarea``

export const Contact = () => {
  return (
    <FormWrapper>
      <FormLabel>
        Nome
        <FormInput type="text" value="name" placeholder="Nome"></FormInput>
      </FormLabel>
      <FormLabel>
        E-mail
        <FormInput type="email" value="email" placeholder="E-mail"></FormInput>
      </FormLabel>
      <FormLabel>
        Telefone
        <FormInput
          type="tel"
          value="telefone"
          placeholder="Telefone"
        ></FormInput>
      </FormLabel>
      <FormLabel>
        Mensagem
        <FormTextArea></FormTextArea>
      </FormLabel>
    </FormWrapper>
  )
}
